name: Dr. Omar Ali
description: Dr. Angelo Cardarelli is an Italian Oral Surgeon.He graduated from l’Aquila University and he specialized in Oral Surgery in Rome “Sapienza” University. He focuses on surgical treatment of impacted teeth using piezoelectric device and atrophic jaws rehabilitation using a reduced numbers of implants.He do many courses and lectures around the world about those topics. He work in his Clinic “Clinica Cardarelli” in the South of Italy with his brother and father, and also in Milan at San Raffaele Hospital as Scientific Advisor and he is Adjunct Professor at ”Vita Salute University” in Milan.
